text: Emiliano Aguirre Enríquez (5 October 1925 – 11 October 2021) was a Spanish paleontologist. He was a member of the Academy of Fine Arts and History 'Institución Fernán González'. Aguirre died on 11 October 2021, six days after his 96th birthday. ==References== Category:1925 births Category:2021 deaths Category:Spanish scientists Category:Paleontologists
